sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant KServeCtrl as KServe Controller
    participant ODHCtrl as ODH Model Controller
    participant KnativeSvc as Knative Serving
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant IstioGW as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>8080/TCP mTLS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP mTLS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation (KServe Serverless Mode)

    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>KServeCtrl: Watch event
    KServeCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Knative Service<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>ODHCtrl: Watch InferenceService event<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Istio VirtualService<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Istio Gateway<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create PeerAuthentication (STRICT mTLS)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMeshMember<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create AuthConfig (if auth enabled)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,S3: Inference Request Flow

    User->>Router: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+ edge termination<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    Router->>IstioGW: Forward request<br/>mTLS
    IstioGW->>Activator: Route via VirtualService<br/>mTLS (mesh internal)
    Activator->>Predictor: Inference request<br/>HTTP mTLS
    Predictor->>S3: Load model artifacts<br/>HTTPS AWS Access Key
    S3-->>Predictor: Model data
    Predictor-->>Activator: Prediction result
    Activator-->>IstioGW: Response
    IstioGW-->>Router: Response mTLS
    Router-->>User: JSON response HTTPS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Storage Configuration Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create data connection Secret<br/>opendatahub.io/dashboard=true
    K8sAPI-->>ODHCtrl: Watch Secret event (StorageSecretReconciler)
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: List all data connection Secrets<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>ODHCtrl: Return Secrets list
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create/Update storage-config Secret<br/>Aggregated credentials (JSON)
    K8sAPI-->>Predictor: Mount storage-config Secret
    Predictor->>S3: Access model storage<br/>Credentials from storage-config

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Monitoring Configuration

    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create RoleBinding (prometheus-ns-access)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAPI: Prometheus Operator watches ServiceMonitors
    K8sAPI-->>K8sAPI: Update Prometheus config
    K8sAPI->>ODHCtrl: Scrape /metrics endpoint<br/>8080/TCP HTTPS Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Predictor: Scrape model metrics<br/>HTTPS Bearer Token
